Flaming Fire Conditions
For the two fibrous materials in the flaming condition, stone wool and glass wool, ignition was not observed even above 800°C. For the four foams, PUR, PIR, PhF and EPS, ignition and steady flaming was achieved for the two flaming fire conditions and for intermediate ventilation conditions.

